snippet.textDisplay: when i was little, my uncle Ronny would use noodles like that. the first time i ever seen em i thought they looked like snot. my uncle got offended when i told him so he said "never say ew or gross to something you've never tried before. you never know you might like it." he then proceeded to shove a big mouthful into my mouth. I don't think I've ever had such an amazing texture/flavor combination in my mouth. this took me back to when i was like 9, and I loved every bit of it.
